OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew visits Zambia to find out how
OL,8,Fmuch impact its drought is having on
OL,9,Fcrucial crops
OL,11,FWords by Rhiannon Hopley
OL,13,FZambia is facing its worst drought in
OL,14,F40 years, with a lack of rain leading
OL,15,Fto a 50% crop failure across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,FAround 9.8 million people across 84 of
OL,19,Fthe country's 116 districts have been
OL,20,Faffected and food insecurity is
OL,21,Fgrowing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
