OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,FThis is a problem because 80% of
OL,7,Fpeople here rely on agriculture for
OL,8,Ftheir livelihood.
OL,10,FIn Western Province where the drought
OL,11,Fhas hit badly, we meet Nyambe Nyambe,
OL,12,Fa 21-year-old farmer with a two-year-
OL,13,Fold daughter to care for. She has lost
OL,14,Fall her crops.
OL,16,F"The crop failure this year has been
OL,17,Fdevastating," she told us.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
