OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,F"When you compare it to past years,
OL,7,Fthere's always at least some harvest
OL,8,Feven when the weather has been bad.
OL,9,FBut this year, I have lost everything.
OL,10,FThey all dried up."
OL,12,FThe lack of food has driven her to
OL,13,Feating leaves from around the edge of
OL,14,Fthe field that she previously never
OL,15,Fknew were edible and unripe mangoes
OL,16,Ffrom the trees.
