OL,6,FWe are coming to the end of an El Nino
OL,7,Fweather cycle which naturally brings
OL,8,Fdrier conditions to Central Africa.
OL,9,FBut the situation is being exacerbated
OL,10,Fby the effects of climate change as
OL,11,Fthe country's resilience is worn down.
OL,13,FAnother farmer in the village, 43-year-
OL,14,Fold Ngebe Njamba, tells us it is the
OL,15,Fworst drought he has seen in his
OL,16,Fentire life and that he is feeling the
OL,17,Fchange.
OL,26,@nD@eTw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
