OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,F"Compared to my childhood and how we
OL,7,Fused to farm then, it is way more
OL,8,Fdifficult now. I lost all my crops.
OL,9,FI'm worried about hunger. I'm worried
OL,10,Fabout what I will do," he said.
OL,12,FMaize is the staple crop of Zambia,
OL,13,Faccounting for more than two thirds of
OL,14,Fthe calorie intake of the nation and
OL,15,Fis the basis of the national food
OL,16,Fnshima, a thick porridge with
OL,17,Fvegetables.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@VO]
