OL,6,FHowever, maize is not surviving well
OL,7,Fin the drought conditions and nearly
OL,8,F2.2 million hectares of it have been
OL,9,Flost, according to government figures.
OL,11,FIn the Kalabo district in the west of
OL,12,Fthe country, where temperatures at
OL,13,Fthis time of year sit in the high 30s,
OL,14,Fthe lack of maize growth means it is
OL,15,Fbeing brought to the region on relief
OL,16,Ftrucks.
OL,18,FPeople queue for hours in the sun to
OL,19,Fget vouchers to purchase it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
