OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,FNalishuwa Maswabi is six months
OL,7,Fpregnant and for the last three
OL,8,Fmornings she's walked for two hours to
OL,9,Fget to the district office to try and
OL,10,Fregister for the support.
OL,12,F"I'm really worried about my baby. I
OL,13,Fam not so sure of what will happen
OL,14,Fbecause I've been hungry for days,"
OL,15,Fshe told us.
OL,17,FZambia is one of southern Africa's
OL,18,Fmain producers and exporters of maize.
OL,19,FHowever, this year, even commercial
OL,20,Ffarmers are struggling.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
