OL,6,FAround 85% of the country's
OL,7,Felectricity comes from hydropower and
OL,8,Fthe drought has led to reservoir
OL,9,Flevels falling to an historic low,
OL,10,Fresulting in rolling power outages.
OL,12,FGraham Rae is a large scale commercial
OL,13,Ffarmer. This year, he can only
OL,14,Firrigate half his crops as he cannot
OL,15,Fpower the irrigation pumps.
OL,17,FHe said: "Yields have reduced most
OL,18,Fdefinitely. Maize and wheat are down
OL,19,Ffifty percent. All of that has
OL,20,Fimpacted on our profitability. Power
OL,21,Fhas tripled in cost.
OL,26,@yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
