OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,F"I would say in my farming history
OL,7,Fthis is the worst year I've seen."
OL,9,FThe country is hoping for the rains
OL,10,Fwhich should come in October and
OL,11,FNovember ` but even if they do, the
OL,12,Fharvest won't be ready until February
OL,13,Fat the earliest, creating a hunger gap
OL,14,Fin the interim.
OL,16,FThere is also a risk that the rains
OL,17,Fcould be heavy and with the ground as
OL,18,Fhard and dry as it is, that could lead
OL,19,Fto the type of severe flooding seen by
OL,20,Fother nations in the region like Kenya.
