OL,6,FIt could end up washing this year's
OL,7,Fcrops and topsoil away leading the
OL,8,Ffurther disaster.
OL,10,FAt Yuka Mission Hospital in the west
OL,11,Fof the country, they are preparing
OL,12,Fbeds in anticipation of an influx of
OL,13,Fmalnutrition cases.
OL,15,F"The situation is tricky and
OL,16,Fworrisome" says Brian Nyambe, a
OL,17,Fnutrition specialist at the hospital.
