OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,F"We are seeing a lot of cases
OL,7,Fescalating from the drought situation
OL,8,Fin the country. We don't know how the
OL,9,Frainy season will treat us, so even
OL,10,Fpeople who have had time to cultivate
OL,11,Fcrops will have to wait for them to
OL,12,Fgrow.
OL,14,F"We still have some months to come
OL,15,Fwhere people will be without food," he
OL,16,Fadded.
