OL,6,FAid agencies are working with the
OL,7,Fgovernment to mitigate the effects of
OL,8,Fdrought. UNICEF's Scaling up Nutrition
OL,9,FProgramme has trained local community
OL,10,Fvolunteers to spot children who may be
OL,11,Fat risk of malnourishment and send
OL,12,Fthem to clinics.
OL,14,FIt allows early intervention. The
OL,15,Fchildren are given therapeutic food
OL,16,Ffull of nutrients. So far it is
OL,17,Fworking to keep cases of severe
OL,18,Fmalnutrition down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
