OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,FMainza Kawanu from UNICEF Zambia says
OL,7,Fthe support is crucial: "The climate
OL,8,Fcrisis is not just an environmental
OL,9,Fcatastrophe, it is a child rights
OL,10,Femergency. 45% of children in Zambia
OL,11,Fare getting one meal a day.
OL,13,F"UNICEF is providing life-saving
OL,14,Fsupplies, such as ready-to-use
OL,15,Ftherapeutic foods to children in need.
OL,16,FPreventing moderate malnutrition cases
OL,17,Fto transition into severe acute
OL,18,Fmalnutrition cases is critical to
OL,19,Fprevent a full-blown crisis."
