OL,6,FEducation is also being affected.
OL,7,FSandy Shawa the headteacher of Chipapa
OL,8,FPrimary School in Chilanga says they
OL,9,Fare seeing a drop in pupil numbers as
OL,10,Fchildren are forced to stay home from
OL,11,Fschool to search out food and water
OL,12,Ffor their families.
OL,14,FThose that do come are often hungry,
OL,15,Faffecting their concentration levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
