OL,6,F"As a teacher I am worried because we
OL,7,Fare likely to have most of the
OL,8,Flearners dropping out from school
OL,9,Fbecause of hunger. This is the
OL,10,Fchallenge. If this is not controlled
OL,11,Fnow, then we are going to have a
OL,12,Fdisaster in terms of school going
OL,13,Fchildren."
OL,15,FThe school is currently providing a
OL,16,Ffeeding programme supported by the
OL,17,Fcharity World Vision as it tries to
OL,18,Fkeep its pupils in school as much as
OL,19,Fit can.
