OL,6,FZambia produces the same amount of
OL,7,Femissions in a year as the UK does in
OL,8,Ften days. The government would like
OL,9,Fsupport from the international
OL,10,Fcommunity to help provide funds for
OL,11,Fthe country to update its
OL,12,Finfrastructure in the face of a
OL,13,Fchanging climate.
OL,15,F"We're in a precarious position with
OL,16,Ffood security. The agricultural sector
OL,17,Fis dependant on rainfall and we
OL,18,Fhaven't had it" said Gabriel Pollen,
OL,19,Fthe National Coordinator for Zambia's
OL,20,FDisaster Management and Mitigation
OL,21,FUnit.
