OL,3,C'Climate change-caused' drought leaves
OL,4,CZambians on cusp of hunger crisis
OL,6,F"Developing countries like Zambia are
OL,7,Fbearing the brunt of climate change.
OL,8,FWe're at the frontlines of the impact
OL,9,Fof climate change as we see in this
OL,10,Fdrought.
OL,12,F"Developed nations need to transition
OL,13,Ffrom mere talking to action on the
OL,14,Fground. The support we receive at the
OL,15,Fmoment is to help alleviate the
OL,16,Fimmediate issues like food shortages
OL,17,Fbut we need more long-term support to
OL,18,Fbuild resilience to help us better
OL,19,Fwithstand climate change."
