OL,6,FFor now, Zambia awaits and hopes for
OL,7,Fthe rains ` but even if they do come,
OL,8,Fit will provide short term relief.
OL,10,FClimate change is affecting the way of
OL,11,Flife here, demanding a raft of
OL,12,Fchanges. It will not be a quick fix.
